revisions.rev:
This is a list of [[laws]] from around the world permitting or outlawing [[homosexual]] behaviour (see [[sodomy laws]]). The list is arranged alphabetically by [[continent]] (with the [[Middle East]] listed seperately).

==List of Homosexuality Laws==

